PayPal - beta
=============================================

This CodeIgniter library handles payments via PayPal including IPN responses.

Modification and fixes of Ran Aroussi code (http://codeigniter.com/wiki/PayPal_Lib/) which was based on the PayPal PHP class by Micah Carrick including:

- Deprecated eregi() fix
- Added file or db logging config option
- Added logging individual Paypal ipn fields
- Included PayPal IPN field db schema

Extra
-----

If you'd like to request changes, report bug fixes, or contact
the developer of this library, please email <orattue[at]toomanytabs.com>